snippet.title: Blake: The Visual Novel official game trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1538680/Blake_The_Visual_Novel/

Graphic Novel meets Visual Novel in this sci-fi/thriller interactive story. 

As incriminating events start to revolve around him, experience the dark, mind-bending, truth-seeking journey of Blake and his pivotal transformation into a vigilante.
